      • checkClientSecret

        protected void checkClientSecret​(BaseClient client,
                                 BaseClientStore store)
        This takes the client created from the JSON that came in the request and goes to the correct store, grabs the client with that ID stashed there and then checks that the secrets match. This means that the argument's secret is the actual secret and the stored client's secret is a hash of it.
        Parameters:
        client -
        store -
